{"tid":98411,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"推薦幾套現實災難救援漫畫（已完結）（詳細介紹）","createTime":"2017-01-28T11:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T13:35:05.000Z","uid":79181,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fbbd8419587be0ee851006772e16433e0eaa6406","tid":98411,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:31:03.000Z","msg":"海猿等等係香港多人熟悉嘅救援漫畫我就唔係度介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.特殊救救難隊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8o8zes9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8o8zes9.jpg&h=8e78d3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/285k0cK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F285k0cK.jpg&h=c4e9bb09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/193013_df01f56fd793d092d45c56aec33f51f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F193013_df01f56fd793d092d45c56aec33f51f7.jpg&h=9cfa7684&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左係日本海域進行救援工作，同時係代表日本嘅國際救援部隊。依部漫畫講述男主成長加入部隊過程、日本國際救難隊嘅成立、協助其他經驗不足嘅島國設立相關部隊，當中仲有南亞海潚。<br />\n<br />\n2.海難英雄（海獅）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/181131_c2401ea03f772c37a69f069cb5c7276e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F181131_c2401ea03f772c37a69f069cb5c7276e.jpg&h=7a38b3ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/181149_d60f10c2cf03f43d791b0fadfeee9f17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F181149_d60f10c2cf03f43d791b0fadfeee9f17.jpg&h=b5430a65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y63478B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY63478B.jpg&h=f4055086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不同於上面嘅特殊救難隊/海上保安廳，依套係講負責海難現場善後、打撈工作嘅私營民間企業，有些時候甚至會聯合海上保安廳進行救援。順帶一提，我地香港都有類似嘅打撈公司可以係google搵到。另外，依套漫畫就係講現場善後嘅危險、潛水打撈技術、海難影響航運經濟/船運公司嘅立場利益。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3.Dr.DMAT〜瓦礫下的醫師<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/182232_fa3c15b4e26929b18b3e9108dcec1e28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F182232_fa3c15b4e26929b18b3e9108dcec1e28.jpg&h=e344effc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/182337_c82443b561d4cf256c8bc846c4bc9c2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F182337_c82443b561d4cf256c8bc846c4bc9c2e.jpg&h=c328dbcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ohs89Un.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fohs89Un.jpg&h=7338602b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陸地上例如地震、大型火災水災/交通事故、恐襲等等嘅急救單位，但係由醫院當值醫生人手緊急調派到現場進行急救/傷檢分類，唔知道香港有冇依種突發事故嘅機制呢？ 故事講述急救部隊面對嘅壓力、隨機應變力、快速判斷、家屬怪責/醫生自身嘅內疚、仲有各種醫療急救知識、資源短缺/增加器材資金人手所面對嘅政治阻力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4.死化妝師<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/183418_00c899a688b0adf5ffedf5977937d26a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F183418_00c899a688b0adf5ffedf5977937d26a.jpg&h=b48e7339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8E99fa6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8E99fa6.jpg&h=63770ec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xEr99k9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxEr99k9.jpg&h=672eaf3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比起急救部隊更加後方處理屍體工作嘅單位，好多時災難事故現場器材/技術/人手不足，導致屍體處理工作馬虎，佢地就係負責接手處理直接面對死亡。依套漫畫可以反映出香港殯儀業技術嘅落後，反思香港社會對殯儀嘅守舊迷信，亦可以讓讀者了解屍體處理嘅工驟/技術、成為死化妝師嘅修讀過程。咁岩我睇依套漫畫嘅時候屋企亦都有人過身，係依本漫畫陪我渡過痛苦嘅時期。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5.烈焰赤子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0W2284.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0W2284.jpg&h=f906133d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LOfGEix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLOfGEix.jpg&h=6bf52220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主角成為世界知名消防員的故事。畫風、入面設備/技術都比較舊，不過當中嘅熱血同矛盾吸引我一口氣睇完。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完介紹希望大家會對依幾套漫畫有興趣，更加了解依方面單位嘅困難。<br />\n如果你係已經投身從事相關工作/準備畢業加入，亦希望依幾套漫畫可以減輕你嘅壓力/困惑、保持你對工作嘅熱誠/積極。<br />\n如果你係佢地嘅家屬，希望可以令你地更了解更明白佢地嘅工作同犧牲、付出嘅時間，支持佢地多啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當中盡力救人、保護自己性命、犧牲少數等等嘅矛盾同內疚，或者英雄主義/團隊合作/服從命令，都好值得我地思考。<br />\n<br />\n近年已經好少有依類型漫畫出現，當中作者親身去趣材嘅照片/訪談亦值得學習，真係好想再有更多可以了解到現今技術、知識，又有劇情嘅漫畫出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"b8c64a5a4ff2809187dec21737b8c2d2caffc5f6","tid":98411,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:32:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f397082bbb49fd84de1181d91c1c5ae2f254259","tid":98411,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:41:12.000Z","msg":"海猿呢？ 不過漫畫灰到爆, 同電影係2回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04839e5a80782cf0ba48882f2f57329957616dcd","tid":98411,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:42:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海猿呢？ 不過漫畫灰到爆, 同電影係2回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一句未講左海猿太多人識同睇過所以唔介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafe5a6d4743e91d471a0031399d64e0b018cb1f","tid":98411,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:43:13.000Z","msg":"第5個本港版叫我們的消消防員"},{"pid":"e0ff20cf458741bbd6a76fa2a3fa6373b9a5c7bc","tid":98411,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:55:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07f386e13a01d4c6c3012f33e6f72e0f553500bf","tid":98411,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>海猿呢？ 不過漫畫灰到爆, 同電影係2回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一句未講左海猿太多人識同睇過所以唔介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我估好多人只係睇過戲無睇過漫畫"},{"pid":"7a0ce920012fe012c851a267644901cac6fa06b6","tid":98411,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:04:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d7cbc3483cbb26499b6d55c196729642f1dee35","tid":98411,"uid":882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"第五果套咩譯名黎 聽都未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n細過聽開 我們的消防員<br />\n<br />\n前半段好睇 最尾救山火 同 外國鐵路 over左"},{"pid":"bd2d31eaa073315d58cf13eaa70c126ed29bdfb5","tid":98411,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:20:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2ee407e44e9c03abb5dc7f5bb6bee7ad4a0f5a2","tid":98411,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死化妝師，有興趣睇<br />\nDr 咩咩果部畫功睇落唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nThanks 樓主"},{"pid":"b23f49aeb13bb8115a9e92e5228f1ff34fa7c152","tid":98411,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T15:06:12.000Z","msg":"樓豬高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d529060ba0d180f80f2a9968cfa01944f9e235","tid":98411,"uid":46927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78f3293779eb64f6382bc02a6c79172e109028e","tid":98411,"uid":38192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T13:35:05.000Z","msg":"早排睇完 石塚真一 岳<br />\n主要講述槍岳一帶山難救援。<br />\n十分寫實，漫畫中不會寫遇到山難的人會被主角救返。<br />\n相反，十之八九的個案，主角都是無力回天，遇難者最終命喪。<br />\n但書中對山野遇難，如何求生，救援人員如何救援，有很深刻的描述。推介。"}]}